ProfessorShengisspecializedintheoryofcurriculumandintrction,especiallyininstructionaltheoryanddesign,hisresearchworkisacknowledgedtohaveachievedtheleadinglevelinthecountry.Hiscourseof&ldquo;instructionaltheoryanddesign&rdquo;haswontherewardsof&ldquo;NationalFineCurriculum&rdquo;,6relatedtextbooksandbookshavebeenpublished.ProfessorShengisnowinchargeof6researchprojectsfundedbyprovincialgovernmentandministries.HehaswonProvincialGovernmentExcellentTeachingAchievementFirstPrizeAwardtwice,SecondPrizeAwardthreetimes,NationalEducationScienceResearchExcellentAchievementSecondPrizeAwardtwice,andwashonoredwithNationalHigherEducation&ldquo;BaoGang&rdquo;ExcellentTeacherAwardin2001.
